In this statement, the President of the United States wishes Nelson Mandela a happy 92nd birthday and expresses gratitude for Mandela's vision, leadership, and spirit. The President also acknowledges the first annual Nelson Mandela International Day and encourages people to engage in acts of service in honor of Mandela's 67 years of sacrifice and service. The statement emphasizes the importance of following Mandela's example in giving back to communities, nations, and the world.